female (40, 42–44) and male (41): 40, 41. Spinnerets, general view; 42. Anterior lateral spinnerets; 43. Posterior median spinnerets; 44. Posterior lateral spinnerets. Abbreviations: Ac—aciniform gland spigot; Cy—cylindrical gland spigot; mAmp—minor ampullate gland spigot; MAmp—major ampullate gland spigot; Pi—piriform gland spigot.
</paragraph>
